title: Chompy (disambiguation)

properties.name: description
properties.value: Chompy can refer to multiple things.

content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Chompy (disambiguation)

Chompy can refer to multiple things.

  • Big Chompy Bird Hunting, the quest
  • Chompy bird hunting, the activity
  • Chompy bird, the hunted monster
    • Jubbly bird, a variant of the Chompy bird
  • Chompy chick, a pet obtained from Chompy bird hunting after the Western Provinces diaries are completed
  • Chompy bird hat, a reward for killing chompy birds
  • Cooked chompy, the result of cooking a raw chompy
  • Raw chompy, a drop from the chompy birds
  • Ruined chompy, a useless item made while cooking a chompy incorrectly
  • Seasoned chompy, a quest item in Big Chompy Bird Hunting
  • Skewered chompy, a raw chompy on an Iron spit
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
